HEADWORD: Meteyard
<hw>Mete"yard`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>metgeard</ets>. See <er>Mete</er> to measure, and <er>Yard</er>
stick.]</ety> <def>A yard, staff, or rod, used as a measure.</def>
